node.title: Body of overdue tramper located on West Coast
node.description: Police say the body of an overdue tramper has been found in the Mt Adams wilderness area, south of Harihari on the West Coast.
node.content:
["Police say the body of an overdue tramper has been found in the Mt Adams wilderness area, south of Harihari on the West Coast.", "", "
Mt Adams wilderness area, West Coast. Photo: Google Maps
", "In a statement, Police said the man was reported missing yesterday after failing to return from a trip.", "A West Coast Search and Rescue team located the body this morning and the body was recovered shortly after.", "Police said the death has been referred to the coroner."]
